text: Aaishi 001. Mujhe exactly yaad nahi kaise pehli baar mille the but uske baad saath hi the. Bahut philosophical baate karta hai tu, tab toh psychology ka course kar rha tha isiliye. Aur uske baad exam ke time pe library mein kam aur ccd mein zyaada baithna. Exams ke beech mein tennis khelna. Lucknow ka trip. Last antaragni mein kurte pehenke nikale the. Rooftop pe discussions. Late night chaupathi jaana, Ishu har baar rota tha par aajaata tha. Aur tera hindi aur English bolne ka unique tareeka humesha funny lagega. Obhiously tu life mein chaapega aur bahut saare trips pe chalenge bullet pe.
author: Satyam  Ralhan

text: Jo main likhne waala tha wahi likh diya, mille swimming mein the , sabko dekhke chutiya bolte the but uske baad thode alag raaste hogaye. Fir bhi semester mein ek do baar dhang ki baat karte the aur kassar poori kar dete the. Mast banda hai tu aur chaapu bhi. Aur dance ki video daalna bey :P
author: Satyam  Ralhan

text: Gupta ji aapke baare mein toh kya hi kehna. Humesha se chaapu insaan. Mere graduate hone ka reason tu bhi hai ek. Pehle bahut shareef samajh liya tha tujhe, bahut badi galti kardi. But baadmein bahut besharam ho gaya tu, start hone ke baad rukta hi nahi tha tu, gussa karo toh hass deta tha. Bahut khela hai FIFA tere saath. Alt f4 toh nahi bhuulunga kabhi. Baaki toh korea mein chaapna aur tere pet ko salaam.
author: Satyam  Ralhan

text: Bhai tu leader hai pata nahi kisko lead karta hai par tu leader hai. Bahut on the point baate karta hai aur saamne waale ki maar bhi leta hai, Shubhankar aur teri baatein sunne mein bahut mazza aata tha aur teri aur Aaishi ke room ki kahani bhi. Cycle bech di ki nahi poore campus ki :P

text: Aur dekh liya kar kiske saamne gaali de rha hai :D :D

text: Aur be kaisa hai be. Kaafi chill insaan hai tu, kissi cheez ki tension nahi leta tha. Atrangi baate karta hai tu kaafi. First year mein football mein mille the uske baad fortnite ka squad bana aur saari football ki treats. Bahut mazze kiye hai tere saath. Aur tu toh pro hai hi ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚. Hall 3 tera doosra room tha , room pe padhe rehta tha. Oat pe aisi hi jaake bala pe naachna yaad rahega. Mama mio, chick blast, kfc , china town sab bahut thoosa hai tere saath. Aur woh waale din 2020 march mein jab bahut kam log the campus mein tab bahut bakchodi kaati thi. Wo holi aur poori raat oat ki rooftop pe telescope se aasmaan ko dekna, gajab ki feel thi. Last night jaldi so gaya tha uska zyaada duukh hai ðŸ˜…ðŸ˜…. Joke maarte rahiyo humesha.

text: Jassi paaji , sacch batau toh good newzz dekhke diljit se tu hi yaad aata hai puura puura, second year mein gensec bann gaya tha kitna khush hua the sab. Football ki treats se leke college mein sports ka enthusiasm ki talks sab yaad hai. Bc tumhari wing hi mast thi , dheere dheere toh sabke saath hi mazze karne lage the.  Uss din haath na toota hota toh tere liye ladta but main poori gawahi di thi. Bahut busy hogaya that jab gensec tha, bada aadmi ekdum. Aur jo astrology club mein mazze kiye hai aur early morning aake movie dekhna tab bahut mazze kiye the. Mujhe to vishwaas nahi hota ki main 8 ghante tere saath car mein baith liya. Bhai trip plan kiya tha kabhi toh karenge
author: Satyam  Ralhan

text: Aur chotu, bhai college shuuru bhi tere saath hua aur khatam bhi. Mini militia ke naam nahi bhuulunga aur screenshots toh ab tak hai. Tu mere se milne nahi aata ya main tere se milne nahi aata yahi chalta tha humara ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚. Mast aadmi hai tu, sab karleta hai aur confidence tagda hai tera, height ke hisaab se kuch zyaada hi hai. Tezz bhaagta hai tu saale ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚. College khatam hone se pehle ek bakchod sa trip maar hi liya bhai. Waapas campus aane ke baad toh din mein 5 5 sports khelna, regular gym bhi jaane lag gaye the, induction waali maggi ka pyaar bahut mast experiences rahe hai. Not sad because it ended but happy because it happened jaisa tu bolta tha. More trips to come bro.
author: Satyam  Ralhan

text: Bhai milla toh pehle bhi tha but end ke din mein mazze aaye, photoshoot mein itni bakchodi ki , kabhi nahi bhuulunga , saala kya evolution tha uss din :P

text: It was by chance ki TA mein group bann gaya tha but haan kya journey thi wo, pata nahi kaise bana tha project. Zyaada saath mein nahi rhe hai but humble hai tu and aakhri dino football bhi khel lete the. All the best aage ke liye yaar.

text: Baaju waale room mein rehta tha but khulta nahi tha kissi se but jab bolna shuuru karta tha toh rukta nahi tha, Tv series aur movies chodke bahar aaya kar, discussion karne. Woh OAT waali talk sabke saath toh kabhi nahi bhuulunga. apne mein mast aadmi hai tu.

text: Baba , humesha aise hi jaana hai tumme, mast banda hai tu, kaam ke time pe focused aur waise kaafi fun. Humesha haste khelte baat karta hai, aise hi rehna, newspaper padhne aaya karta tha aur cricket ka spectator tha main. Baba boi mast ho tum

text: Bhai tu khud joke maarke hass deta tha. Kya hi bolu entertaining hai tu kaafi, Antaragni mein hum log contact khelke mazze le rhe the. text: Bhai one of the guys who has been there from the start, bahut mm khela hai bahut mazze liye hai tumhare. Mere saath har baar group mein phass jaate the buura lagta tha mujhe but couldnt help it. Stress kam liya karo, you are smart and capable and will achieve great things. Tumse zyaada knowledge kissi field mein nahi hai, kissi topic pe toh shaant hojaaya karo. FIFA khelna lecture hall mein kya feel aayi thi and you were crazy enough to play with me. Midsems ke beechmein movie dekhke aana was so fun. Thodi se english seekha deni thi tumhe. Take care bhai aur milte toh hum rahenge hi.
